textAnnotations.description:
Performance is answering 50,000
questions a day. High performance
is doing it for New Yorkers.
High performance. Delivered.
With more than 50,000 calls a day coming
in from people speaking 170 different
languages, New York City needed a way to
field a constant stream of non-emergency
phone requests. We helped the city develop
311, a 24/7 phone and online customer
service center that provides nearly 4,000
services to free up resources and provide
faster customer response times. 125 million
calls later, the city is performing better than
ever. That's high performance, delivered.
consulting technology | outsourcing
accenture
